    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Setting Up Rails With HAML]]></title>
    <link href="http://akkrisan.github.io/blog/blog/2016/02/24/setting-up-rails-with-haml/"/>
    <updated>2016-02-24T17:13:07-06:00</updated>
    <id>http://akkrisan.github.io/blog/blog/2016/02/24/setting-up-rails-with-haml</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ol>
<li><p>Create a new rails project.</p>

<pre><code class="`"> $ rails new projectName
</code></pre></li>
<li><p>Add &lsquo;haml&rsquo; and &lsquo;haml-rails&rsquo; to the Gemfile.</p>

<pre><code class="`"> gem 'haml'
 gem 'haml-rails'
</code></pre></li>
<li><p>In config/application.rb, add the following code inside the Application class:</p>

<pre><code class="`"> config.generators do |g|
   g.template_engine :haml
 end
</code></pre></li>
<li><p>Run bundle install.</p>

<pre><code class="`"> $ bundle install
</code></pre></li>
</ol>

]]></content>
